OL,6,FITV's Tonight programme broadcast on
OL,7,FITV1 and ITVX at 8.30pm on February
OL,8,F20, titled 'Forced Adoption: Britain's
OL,9,FSilent Scandal' explores one of
OL,10,FBritain's darkest social injustices
OL,11,Fand the lifelong consequences.
OL,13,FA bulletin published by the Moral
OL,14,FWelfare Workers' Association in 1964,
OL,15,Fa body representing social workers at
OL,16,Fthe time, shows that mother and baby
OL,17,Fhomes were recommended to prescribe
OL,18,FDES to dry up breast milk.
