OL,6,FThe drug was prescribed to women
OL,7,Facross the world, not just to dry up
OL,8,Fbreast milk but also to treat several
OL,9,Fissues including preventing
OL,10,Fmiscarriages. That was until it was
OL,11,Fwidely withdrawn in the 1970s due to
OL,12,Fits links to cancer.
OL,14,FThe legacy of this so-called 'wonder
OL,15,Fdrug' is far reaching. Around the
OL,16,Fworld there have been hundreds of
OL,17,Fcourt cases as well as government
OL,18,Fapologies and compensation payments to
OL,19,Fthose exposed to it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/23
