OL,6,F"People call it the hidden
OL,7,Fthalidomide, because it is there, we
OL,8,Fknow it is there, but we don't know
OL,9,Fwhat is the size of the problem."
OL,11,FDr Agur wants a full inquiry to
OL,12,Fascertain how many women have been
OL,13,Fexposed to the drug.
OL,15,FAcademics who have studied the drug
OL,16,Festimate anywhere between 10,000 to
OL,17,F300,000 women came into contact with
OL,18,FDESin the UK, although many patients
OL,19,Fwere never told they'd been prescribed
OL,20,Fit.
