OL,6,FIn the decades that followed there
OL,7,Fwere repeated warnings about the
OL,8,Fsafety of DES flagged at the highest
OL,9,Flevel of the health service, but it
OL,10,Fwasn't until the 1970s that it was
OL,11,Fwithdrawn from use after a US
OL,12,Fscientist proved it was carcinogenic.
OL,14,FIn 1967, a letter written to the then
OL,15,FChief Medical Officer from the Welsh
OL,16,FNational School of Medicine, warned
OL,17,Fabout risks of blood clots associated
OL,18,Fwith the drug.
