OL,6,FThese concerns were discussed for
OL,7,Fyears but no clear steps were taken to
OL,8,Faddress this before it was eventually
OL,9,Fphased out in in the 1970s due to its
OL,10,Flinks to cancer.
OL,12,FAlongside its use in mother and baby
OL,13,Fhomes, the hormone was also used in
OL,14,Fthe agricultural sector.
